# Minilab — Decisions Log

> **How to use:** Read the last 20 entries before starting any session.
> Append a new entry at the BOTTOM every time you make an architectural decision.
> Never edit or delete existing entries. This is an append-only audit trail.

## Entry Format
```
---
DATE: YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM:SSZ
DECISION_ID: D-XXXX
CATEGORY: architecture | tooling | schema | security | scope | integration
CONTEXT: What situation required a decision
OPTIONS_CONSIDERED:
  1. [option]
  2. [option]
DECISION: What was chosen and why
DECIDED_BY: claude_code | human (Telegram reply to MSG-XXXX)
TASK_REF: T001 (which task.md task this relates to)
---
```

