DECISION: Three new files. lib/ai/prompts.ts — assembleSystemPrompt() builds 7-section prompt following Section 40 exact order: base rules (6 hard rules + JSON output format), context type rules (RESIDENT vs STAFF/BM), building context (name + local time), user context (name + unit), intent data (Layer 2 fetched data serialised as JSON), tool list (from intent definition). assembleUserMessage() prepends last 3 conversation history messages. lib/ai/hallucination-guard.ts — validateAgentOutput() extracts all case refs (ML-CASE/ML-YYYYMMDD), booking IDs (ML-BK), and monetary amounts (RM xxx) from response, cross-checks against Layer 2 context via recursive scan of FetchedData. Hallucinated refs → requires_bm_approval=true, message replaced with escalation text. lib/ai/specialist-agent.ts — runSpecialistAgent() routes to callDeepSeek() (temp 0.3, json_object mode) or callClaude() (Anthropic Messages API, temp 0.3). Self-confidence thresholds: ROUTINE<0.70, SENSITIVE<0.80, LEGAL<0.90 → auto-queue BM review. Webhook handler now runs full 3-layer pipeline and creates approvals record when BM review needed.
