DATE: 2026-03-19T23:01:00Z
DECISION_ID: D-0080
CATEGORY: architecture
CONTEXT: Missing installment payment module for defaulting residents. Defaulters should be blocked from services until they pay or set up installment plan.
DECISION: New installment module with BM toggle (on/off per building):

  BM CONFIGURES (/bm/settings/collection):
  - Installment enabled: YES/NO
  - Minimum upfront: X% or RM X (whichever is set)
  - Monthly installment: RM X per month
  - Maximum installment period: X months
  - Auto-block access if installment payment missed: YES/NO

  DEFAULTER FLOW (when resident messages WhatsApp/Telegram):
  - AI detects outstanding balance > threshold
  - AI response: "Your account has an outstanding balance of RM X,XXX. Services are limited until payment is made. You can: (1) Pay in full [DuitNow QR], or (2) Apply for installment plan."
  - No other services available — balance query, case creation, booking ALL blocked. Only payment and installment flow works.
  - If resident chooses installment: AI presents the plan: "Pay RM [upfront] now + RM [monthly] for [X] months. Reply AGREE to proceed."
  - Resident agrees → installment_plans record created → BM notified for approval
  - BM approves → access restored immediately → monthly installment tracked
  - Each month: if installment not paid by due date → 7-day grace → access blocked again → AI notifies resident
  - If installment fully paid → normal service restored → collection_accounts cleared

  NEW TABLE: installment_plans (id, unit_id, building_id, total_outstanding, upfront_amount, upfront_paid_at, monthly_amount, total_months, months_paid, next_due_date, status [proposed/active/defaulted/completed], approved_by, created_at)

  AI BEHAVIOR FOR DEFAULTERS:
  - Any intent from defaulter → intercept BEFORE normal routing
  - Response: balance + payment options + installment option
  - ONLY intents allowed: PAYMENT_ENQUIRY, PAYMENT_CLAIM, INSTALLMENT_REQUEST, EMERGENCY
  - EMERGENCY always goes through regardless of payment status
  - This applies to WhatsApp AND Telegram
DECIDED_BY: human
