DECISION_ID: D-0249
CATEGORY: fix
CONTEXT: Deep code review revealed three root causes. (1) Web→Telegram sync code was structurally correct (fires for all paths) but tgSend uses parse_mode:Markdown and AI responses contain unmatched special chars — already stripped in prior commit. Added comprehensive diagnostic logging to verify. (2) Working hours — the REAL root cause was the ai_tools.parameters schema being too vague ("Day to hours mapping") so DeepSeek dumped raw user text as time values instead of extracting structured data. Also parseDayName only matched full day names, not abbreviations, and handler couldn't expand day ranges like "monday-friday". (3) Conversation memory in admin-router only queried web_chat channel, missing Telegram messages.
