DECISION_ID: D-0353
CATEGORY: bug-fix
CONTEXT: PWA functional audit identified 5 remaining data-flow bugs after D-0351/D-0352 fixes. All are response shape mismatches, silently dropped form values, or incorrect count queries.
OPTIONS_CONSIDERED:
  1. Fix each bug individually across multiple sessions — rejected (all identified, batch is more efficient)
  2. Single commit fixing all 5 data-flow issues — selected
DECISION: Fixed 5 PWA data-flow bugs in one commit:
  FIX-1 Announcements response shape + field names: Page handled `data.data` but API returns `{ announcements: [...] }`. Fixed .then() to read `data.announcements`. Also renamed interface field `body` → `content` to match DB column, removed `is_pinned` (not in DB), updated render from `{a.body}` → `{a.content}`. 0 TS errors.
  FIX-2 Incident form category/severity: API hardcoded `incident_type: 'guard_report'` and `severity: 'medium'`. Now reads `category` and `severity` from FormData and uses them (with fallbacks). `guardhouse_incidents.incident_type` and `.severity` are both `text` columns — no enum mapping needed.
  FIX-3 Patrol progress double-count: POST handler counted all `patrol_logs` rows (`count: exact`). Rescanning a beacon inflated done beyond total. Fixed by fetching `beacon_id` rows and deduplicating via `new Set()`. GET handler already used a Set correctly.
  FIX-4 Cleaning date filter MYT timezone: API did `new Date(dateParam)` treating the date as UTC midnight, so MYT day boundaries were 8h off. Fixed to `new Date(\`\${dateParam}T00:00:00+08:00\`)` / `T23:59:59.999+08:00` for correct MYT day window.
  FIX-5 Chat vs task messages: VERIFIED clean — no code change needed. Task comments insert via /api/bm/cases/[id]/messages with `case_id` set. Chat page reads messages filtered by `case_id` via /api/bm/cases/[id]. Channels in DB: `telegram`, `web_chat` (no case_id), `web` (task comments, has case_id). No cross-pollution possible.
  Verification: 0 TypeScript errors. `.content` replaces `.body` in announcements. `category/severity` flow from form to DB. Patrol done uses Set dedup. Cleaning date uses +08:00 offset.
DECIDED_BY: claude_code
TASK_REF: PWA functional audit — 5 data-flow fixes (D-0353)
